{"type": "article", "id": 12109, "title": "超薄无缝钱包", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-15T11:03:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114824JQudWi9U3VrBtNO7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tSeraph &amp; Co 做的这一款钱包是一个超薄对折式钱包，采用的是一整块的软木材料，并像我们小时候玩折纸游戏一样被折叠在一起，整个钱包没有任何拉链或缝合等衔接的痕迹，厚度只有 7 毫米。钱包材料坚韧且防水，同时可回收，能够反复利用。内部设计了五个卡槽和一个放现金的隔层，即使放满东西，仍然可以保持轻薄。<a href=\"http://seraphmade.com/products/origami-cork-bifold-wallet\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135954Kkhqf79T6jWx0nlG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135954t5BLc27039Hz6Opr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359555lcUJduhCWvnr1OK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135955kAQ457hNeFaRxi8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135956zBsSxZhQHwcdpaYA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135957AtQbRI9eLBvlUSn1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}